# scenario.ocp_v1.json is NOT in public/ so it is never served from mit15.com.
# It lives at the project root for local development only (Vite dev server picks
# it up there). Team members who need the OCP scenario run the tool locally or
# use the in-app "Import JSON" file picker with their local copy.
#
# The illustrative scenario is in public/scenario.illustrative.json (symlink)
# and IS served publicly — that is the default view at mit15.com.

